{"tid":355347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊新浪百度涉違反《網絡安全法》被立案調查","createTime":"2017-08-11T08:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T12:01:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8556734cc27f89bddda71694e0e39c2cb5ea1f9d","tid":355347,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"國家網信辦公佈，近日指導北京市、廣東省網信辦分別對騰訊（700）微信、新浪微博、百度貼吧立案，並依法展開調查。受到外圍科技股大跌拖累，騰訊股價今早曾跌近半成，現跌3.74%，報314.4元，成交124.37億元，市值跌穿三萬億大關。<br />\n<br />\n根據網民舉報，經北京市、廣東省網信辦初查，3家網站的微信、微博、貼吧平台分別存在有用戶傳播暴力恐怖、虛假謠言、淫穢色情等危害國家安全、公共安全、社會秩序的信息。<br />\n<br />\n3家網站平台涉嫌違反《網絡安全法》等法律法規，對其平台用戶發佈的法律法規禁止發佈的資訊未盡到管理義務。案件後續進展情況，將由相關地方網信辦予以發佈。<br />\n<br />\n國家網信辦有關負責人表示，網信部門將認真貫徹落實《網絡安全法》等法律法規，進一步加大互聯網資訊內容監管執法力度，依法查處網上各類違法違規行為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57067697&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57067697%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170811&d=pFcolARE4D48kahgiC6wGf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=b86601ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57067697%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170811&h=65b892c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57067697&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170811</a>"},{"pid":"c4888eb4f1e53551136ff949c3a883aab798e76f","tid":355347,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"上個月有個fd起哂綱入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e69955f35d0a56b2c102d6a6ab5e58bb3881da6","tid":355347,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"LM等跌再入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no